 "description": "Fierce, elusive, and approachable only by a maiden — in the strictest sense — pure and noble of heart; maiden-warriors may ride them and be obeyed. Otherwise they shun human contact unless pressed. Attacking, a Unicorn fights as a lance on its first charge and as spear-and-heavy-horse after. Deeply magical: it resists magic as an 11th-level Magic-User, senses enemies at 24\", and once a day carries itself and rider as by a Dimension Door, the full 36\".",
